stlib.datatypes.unit.spatial

Class UnitPointConst

  • java.lang.Object
    • stlib.datatypes.GeneralType
      • stlib.datatypes.unit.UnitObject<PointIF>
        • stlib.datatypes.unit.spatial.UnitPointConst
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<UnitObjectIF<PointIF>>, MovableSpatial, GeneralTypeIF, UnitPointIF, UnitObjectConstIF<PointIF>, UnitObjectIF<PointIF>

    public class UnitPointConst
extends UnitObject<PointIF>
implements UnitPointIF, UnitObjectConstIF<PointIF>
    This class represents 'UnitPointConst' objects and is used for 'MovingPoint' objects with a constant location over a certain period of time.
    Author:
    Markus Fuessel
